comments: Professor O\'Connell is an extremely intelligent man who knows his stuff. His UGS class consisted of 3 essays, however he grades quite hard. You CANNOT bs this class at all. He will scrutinize every word in your writing assignments. So while getting an A is quite difficult, Professor O\'Connell truly teaches how to write at an advanced level.

comments: Great teacher. One of the best teachers ive ever had. Gives very interesting lectures. No problem staying awake. He is engaging. hard A, average B. Gives tons of reading for HW (dont have to do it, doesn\'t quiz if the class talks alot). Always willing to help. Your writing will improve in his class. I strongly recommend him.

comments: GET HIM. Professor O\'Connell might be my favorite teacher I have had at any point in my education. He is incredibly smart, really funny, and his class is very engaging. He promotes a lot of classroom discussion and he gets you thinking about historical events in great depth. He makes naval history more interesting than I thought possible.
